and-Stern electric field better reproduces CIR-driven events. Contrary to what we expect, examination of the HEIDI model results and solar wind data shows that SH-driven events behave more like MC-driven events than CIR-driven storms.},
author = {Katus, R. M. and Liemohn, M. W. and Ionides, E. L. and Ilie, R. and Welling, D. and Sarno-Smith, L. K.},
